data.description: This beautiful 2 story house is just waiting for you to call it home! With a convenient floor plan and laundry on the main floor, you will love the space you have to work with. All four bedrooms are upstairs, along with a full bathroom. In the backyard, a new fence has been installed and a gorgeous landscaping including a pond has been wonderfully maintained. Mature trees give shade and privacy. Schedule a showing and see it for yourself today!
